<p class="ql-align-justify">／在法律允许范围内活动解释权归品牌所有／</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>壹</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>『 一碟牛肉肠，喂大一代老广</strong> <strong>』</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">HUAHUI · LACHANG</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201208/e5d89a6dd5d245cc957198ec855602d4.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">/</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201208/0d5ae83ca04043299426b9f99957350d.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>“冬天的早晨，最适合整碟牛肉肠暖下肠胃”</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">『肠粉皮，要够薄』</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201208/39748b9e027349c7a09376d142c9a5dd.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201208/852e1760e53f4ec9b0183c8b916f3b8c.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201208/78306e870bbc429d9f6b9dd87235ea1c.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">石磨现磨的米浆顺滑度一流，在蒸盘上平铺、抖匀，美味准备就绪~</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">只需蒸上十几秒，肠粉皮便新鲜出炉，瞬间米香四溢。因为肠粉皮够薄，爽口之余又很软滑~</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">『牛肉片，要够厚』</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201208/93eead3f3f064d1b963547de5bc58e0e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">=BEEF=</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">···</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201208/5d10cd80e6b24ea7868c9e19ebd8587e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">一碟牛肉肠，啖啖都有肉才满足！牛肉分量实在，每一片都足够厚足够大，咬起来很是过瘾~</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201208/4a55659ca65b4716be487fb97afe472d.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201208/d3521094023d40d5a599a98de440aab7.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">牛肉现片现蒸，厚度足够，入口嫩滑弹牙，加点酱油就能轻松勾出牛肉香气~</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">『一口满足“嫩、爽、滑”』</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201208/2fc3d8cd926e41dba876e4e86197a8df.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">薄薄的肠粉包裹着厚实弹牙的牛肉片，蘸着酱油一起吃，一口感受舌尖上“嫩、爽、滑”的美味体验~</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">『搭杯豆浆』</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201208/89221300029944bd81e3c0975de92c5d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">///</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201208/d16cd96642d7434bab9d07d70636b857.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">每次吃肠粉都喜欢多加豉油，难免口干...加多杯豆浆就刚好，华辉也太懂我们这些吃货了！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>贰</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">HUAHUI · LACHANG</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">『 腩汁三酱肠粉x香菇鸡皇粥 』</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201208/0ee47a0fb4ec43329cb95a6ac9caf430.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201208/250daa2ee51b49c8b479fbb377ccdf42.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">三酱肠粉的经典不用多说，上至70岁阿嫲，下至3岁学步小童，没有一个广州人不爱这道混酱肠粉！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201208/41f952c0595c473197a8cdc4298ada04.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">辣酱、甜酱、花生酱，三酱加持的肠粉口感丰富，酱香十足！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201208/a7408d3591884bdeaf81192797e89180.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">煲足几个钟的粥底很绵滑，加入鸡腿肉和香菇丝生滚上桌，喝上一口，暖上心头~</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">『 招牌鸡蛋肠x皮蛋瘦肉粥 』</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201208/6a536456d5d6413b876c3af1c7aba706.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201208/816299bc084a4556907ffdf2e3a07a93.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">别小看这份鸡蛋肠！看似平平无奇，一天就能卖出上千份！打入一颗农家土鸡蛋，香滑，绵润，怪不得大家都爱这口朴实的美味...</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201208/1ef27222e7bb4aef81041a6b399314a2.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201208/37a7db0dd63141499664936aa0313c10.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">再来份香喷喷的皮蛋瘦肉粥，味道很浓郁~肠粉+粥，就能饱到扶墙走，打工人、学生党都给我冲起来！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">『 梅菜肉饼饭x椰子炖老鸡 』</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201208/85105737ca944a71a02fc5427c59a813.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">●●●</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201208/a639dd1b17ff4092988a4f8060afe700.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">爱吃肉饼的小伙伴可别错过这款！平时自己做肉饼可太费劲了，还能喝炖汤，营养又美味~</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201208/43c4af0e67404c7ba6774e017340bf33.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">/</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201208/788cd332d068444ca056cc7a4a17881f.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">肉饼很厚实，咀嚼起来肉香和梅干菜香交织，这时再来口椰子鸡汤润润喉，一个字，满足！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">/</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">还没完！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">『 咸蛋腊味饭x无花果南北杏炖猪肺汤 』</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201208/3bafac47eec74cd9880e9111bdf4eac6.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">///</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201208/b7147871e93d4b8cb609689da8557c9f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">揭盖就有腊味香气扑鼻，咸鸭蛋、腊肉、腊肠，都是本广东人爱的！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201208/975ced084f734a559724ab3243decb39.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201208/df31cb787a884a2d96da1f485f51238d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201208/8df94038893c472f9f99f7f2da984cb7.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201208/f7fdb512b06142798b3e54502b562685.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">腊味尝起来很香口，配饭吃真的一流！搭配无花果猪肺汤，也不用担心上火问题~</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>叁</strong></p>
