<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201208/2db222a01dd544388cb4462f74b022b5.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>· CHAOSHAN POP ·</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>「潮人潮品」</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>广州的“小潮汕”，征服无数老广</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>全城潮菜的“课代表”，胶己人都爱吃！</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>地道潮汕味</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">/在法律范围内，活动解释权归商家所有/</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>#01</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201208/d1764566d6d642f48a9718cd28ee47e7.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>广州的“小潮汕”,征服无数老广</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>地道潮汕味</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201208/6ac276ee36e1497daa8dda72de6a5a33.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201208/ea6cb459c9cc441a9a4e02f2ae2a3961.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>「潮人潮品」</strong>主打潮汕菜，厨师都是潮汕人，店里都是<strong>地地道道的潮汕美食</strong>，胶己人都爱吃！“地道潮汕味，好吃也不贵”。<strong>吃潮汕菜就到「潮人潮品」！</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>滋补又营养</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201208/b8efb44b141045a288fae6a3178a8cc0.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201208/a40106cea2424f9a9bf3f246ee5505b1.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>石橄榄猪肚煲乳鸽，金不换罗氏虾煲鸡</strong>强势来袭！营养又滋补，是冬季养生佳品。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>#02</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201208/d1764566d6d642f48a9718cd28ee47e7.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>错过等一年</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>石橄榄猪肚煲乳鸽</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201208/c63264779826481595a87df04769c930.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">冬季养生佳品：<strong>石橄榄猪肚煲乳鸽</strong>，精选珍贵的石橄榄与新鲜猪肚、乳鸽一同慢火熬煮，<strong>煮出来的汤清甜回甘</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>采用当季石橄榄</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201208/8f6940b725a44126915e65346466bdbd.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">石橄榄是潮汕地区特有的<strong>珍贵草本植物</strong>，很有营养价值，还有“仙桃”之称，而这个季节的石橄榄很适合煲汤，<strong>秋冬干燥季节必备！</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>精选优质乳鸽&amp;猪肚</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201208/589709e432fe4790b4b99bf2764ca6aa.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">CHAOSHAN POP</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201208/609b9529a5d645b8937cb303fd2d73df.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201208/cf4bfb78a8064ced98ea4046b8582b9a.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">还有<strong>妙龄乳鸽，新鲜猪肚</strong>加持，使得汤鲜上加鲜。鲜嫩的乳鸽、爽脆的猪肚，吸收了汤底里的精华，<strong>肉质鲜甜弹牙。</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201208/2c7c5072daf042a0995057790044bc74.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201208/3205de8fa0af4172b821301d3b62eca0.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">\\\\\\\</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">///</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201208/34722fc47b194e119967b013580bcb2b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201208/cb529191bb9049bca4a0e6200b4c5b90.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">蘸上店里特制的酱料，<strong>把乳鸽和猪肚的鲜香发挥得淋漓尽致。</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>汤水浓郁，鲜甜回甘</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201208/b8efb44b141045a288fae6a3178a8cc0.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201208/2b9b8869aae643bab8febf3595cc0f10.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">汤水透明中微微带有乳白色，清香四溢，越煮越香。品一口浓郁的清汤，<strong>入口清甜还带有乳鸽香</strong>，随后紧跟着<strong>甘甜</strong>，<strong>仿佛身心都被治愈了。</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>金不换罗氏虾煲鸡</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201208/126a1268827648d58f1f30a258c8260e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">这款菜品也是<strong>秋冬必吃</strong>的美食！选用潮汕特有的草本植物<strong>金不换</strong>，其特殊香味与<strong>走地胡须鸡、罗氏虾</strong>完美结合，<strong>一口就能惊艳你的味蕾！</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201208/e25b78bcdb9545f18bfb26887069c74a.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">///</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201208/d8ee815b1e204cca904104d9560614e8.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">精选营养丰富的新鲜罗氏虾，与走地胡须鸡一起爆炒，高温瞬间将虾的鲜香和鸡肉香味紧锁，<strong>使得虾和鸡外表香脆，内里鲜嫩且入味。</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201208/a40106cea2424f9a9bf3f246ee5505b1.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201208/d518242d814646169ae27378951964d3.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">\\\\\\\</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">///</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201208/d177a6e1d8fd4cce86cd66cac998eb97.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>鸡肉紧实嫩滑，虾肉口感鲜嫩，</strong>酱汁混合着肉的鲜甜迅速攻占口腔，<strong>口口生香！</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201208/684647d01dff40f9a16636c8ab02171c.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">每只虾手掌般大小，还超多虾子，<strong>虾头爆膏爆黄，口感鲜美得像蟹黄般浓郁，好吃到连壳都有味！</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201208/89c4e573f0b74ef5ac473e7e5de833c4.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">///</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201208/c4d3ffee53514e47a6a06e82063db48b.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>堪称绝配的“海陆cp”，虾和鸡相互提味，鲜味提升了一个度。</strong>好吃到连配菜都不能放过，萝卜吸收了汤汁的精华，非常入味！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>#03</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201208/d1764566d6d642f48a9718cd28ee47e7.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>地道潮汕味</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>蒜蓉海鲜拼盘</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201208/953add483d42499b8a9569990a8431ff.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">蒜蓉海鲜拼盘满满的塞满了<strong>青口、带子、圣子、基围虾、扇贝和海鲜菇。</strong>多味争鲜，鲜嫩的海鲜伴着蒜蓉粉丝一起吃，满口鲜甜的海鲜味！<strong>份量超足，满满的鲜味萦绕你的味蕾。</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201208/d4dcb7c5b3b8417fa69e6de1be8528e1.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201208/18db1f4315fe4ed7bf92ffa27ef95390.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">使用原始的清蒸做法，还有蒜蓉加持，还原了海鲜的“鲜”味！最后淋上特制的热油锅，<strong>每口都是恰到好处的鲜香。</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201208/65461281de49419a91d6b0879a9acd95.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201208/7aa0dfeaed464babae79dd58a5d52118.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201208/46cd0ff484c44f218e0f3674615cbcc5.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201208/8a572fda2dd7414babd7cb069d04ce1e.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">肉多个头大的青口<strong>新鲜嫩滑无腥味</strong>，一口咬下去大大的满足感；“海鲜之极”的带子鲜甜至极；扇贝基围虾颜色红艳，肉质弹牙鲜嫩。<strong>最后再嗦一口吸收了海鲜味的粉丝，简直鲜美入魂。</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>潮州老菜脯肉沫粥</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201208/4cf8dda932b24c8082c4d51e0e165410.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">封存几十年的陈年菜脯和肉沫粥两者的混合更是相得益彰。<strong>浓稠入味，飘来阵阵酸香，瞬间打开你的胃口！</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201208/2f878802923947c983cb13fe76971145.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201208/7b3f2e4866444874aa83e3abc1e1ae52.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">\\\\\\\</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">///</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201208/6287e162d59047aeb336b8a256f62192.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>粥浓稠绵密，飘香四溢</strong>，适中的咸香有带又一点独特的酸味，吃的每一口都是享受。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>卤水拼盘</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201208/1f87594ff9c6416c9ffbe53fac0b28e0.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">一定不能错过潮汕的卤味，特别是这盘卤鹅拼盘。用南姜熬制，<strong>不仅能让鹅肉更加入味，还能锁住鹅肉的肉质。</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201208/000552ad4a2348d29d4b240c54c73a2d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201208/d0f0e6d325d94f969712e60f2341579e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201208/6a5ae6c0b28b40b9a044fd37de35010f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201208/6473553b76844af8a19426d85f59c7ee.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201208/98ef9e752aad4f7fad98085eca66100f.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201208/c7af544a345e403c803d3f7ac5503432.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">被卤水充分炮制过的鹅肉，每一口都尝到卤水汁和鹅肉充分相融的滋味，<strong>肉质酥烂，肥而不腻，味道绝！</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>土豪蚝仔烙</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201208/f568909dc13843839e889ea16dad20b6.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>潮汕小吃的C位担当——蚝仔烙，</strong>精选珍珠蚝、鲜虾仁、九肚鱼、鲜干鱿等多种材料放进油锅，煎炸至两面金黄，<strong>外酥内嫩！</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201208/6547df52176c4ffd80cad157864e8715.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201208/3e33321df97043ea87e5105e82934545.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">\\\\\\\</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">///</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201208/bf16a56c1c8e47959094ee22f155fdd4.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">随便切开，满满都是白玉般的蚝仔，<strong>每一口都能吃到鲜嫩肥美的蚝仔，</strong>再沾点鱼露！<strong>外皮还香脆十足，外脆内嫩，一口就爱上了！</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>潮市荷叶夹</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201208/22f563049a574dcba8bf4fca5bddcc1a.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201208/7ffbf2392c4c4ef69fa1e988a267d47c.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">这款就像<strong>“潮式汉堡包”</strong>一样，精选腌制过的<strong>上等五花肉</strong>，配上新鲜蔬菜和荷叶饼一同夹着吃，别有一番风味~</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201208/953d028287b1494db518431fdd6cbe3e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">营养好味的潮式炒饭、爱心煎蛋、各式当季水果。<strong>营养均衡，摆盘精致，小朋友看了胃口大开！</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>#04</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201208/d1764566d6d642f48a9718cd28ee47e7.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>一秒闪现潮汕街头</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201208/0881568fca6744d386f736acc3d8018a.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
