<p class="ql-align-justify">CHAOSHAN POP</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201208/8cef7b9fd8b7470fb86b79c8e38cd8dc.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">店里的装修是<strong>潮汕的居民屋风格</strong>，还把潮汕民居老厝搬进来了，<strong>仿佛一秒闪现潮汕。</strong>还有干净整洁的开放式厨房，吃得更安心！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201208/bd42810a8d344318bc617e6c42c7892d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
